  "name": "tg_raman_ecoli_fermentation",
  "description": "\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tDataset Card for TG-Raman Spectra from E. coli Cultivation\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tDataset Summary\n\t\n\nThis dataset contains offline Raman spectra collected from the cell containing samples during the cultivation of Escherichia coli W3110. Measurements were performed using Time-Gated Raman Spectroscopy (TG-Raman) to suppress background fluorescence from the complex cultivation media via temporal separation.\nThe dataset corresponds to a bioreactor cultivation involving a 10-hour batch phase followed… See the full description on the dataset page: https://huggingface.co/datasets/chlange/tg_raman_ecoli_fermentation.",
  "alternateName": [
    "chlange/tg_raman_ecoli_fermentation",
    "TG-Raman Spectra E. coli Cultivation"
  ],
  "creator": {
    "@type": "Person",
